 Green Day 正在预告《Dookie》30 周年纪念计划https://www.nme.com/news/music/green-day-are-teasing-dookie-30th-anniversary-plans-3480467?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=green-day-are-teasing-dookie-30th-周年纪念计划Will RichardsWed, 09 Aug 2023 12:59:15 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3480467 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/green-day-1994-getty-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="绿日" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/green-day-1994-getty-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/green-day-1994-getty-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/green-day-1994-getty-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/green-day-1994-getty-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/green-day-1994-getty-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/green-day-1994-getty-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>明年初该专辑将庆祝其重要生日</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/green-day-are-teasing-dookie-30th-anniversary-plans-3480467">Green Day 正在调侃“Dookie”30 周年纪念计划的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/green-day-1994-getty-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="绿日" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/green-day-1994-getty-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/green-day-1994-getty-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/green-day-1994-getty-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/green-day-1994-getty-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/green-day-1994-getty-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/green-day-1994-getty-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/green-day">Green Day</a>的标志性专辑《Dookie》明年初将迎来 30 岁生日，乐队已经开始酝酿周年纪念计划。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/green-day-interview-father-of-all-motherfuckers-2020-donald-trump-billie-eilish-2606230">大读物——绿日：“我们过着我们一无所有的生活”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这张专辑于 2024 年 2 月 1 日发行，乐队似乎准备通过一系列庆祝活动来纪念这张专辑。</p><p>目前，预告片相当模糊，只有主题标签#Dookie30 和录音带照片，但在 30 周年纪念日之前肯定会分享更多计划。</p><p>请参阅下面的第一个预告片。 </p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="qme" dir="ltr"><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f440.png" alt="👀" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Dookie30?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Dookie30</a> <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f440.png" alt="👀" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://t.co/9asAgYWFAq">pic.twitter.com/9asAgYWFAq</a></p><p> - 绿日 (@GreenDay) <a href="https://twitter.com/GreenDay/status/1689012361204731906?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 8 月 8 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>早在 2019 年，乐队就在马德里的一场演出中<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/green-day-played-dookie-full-last-night-madrid-watch-2562999">完整演奏了《Dookie》，</a>令歌迷们大吃一惊。这位流行朋克老将在周末 MTV EMA 之前的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/green-day-tour-surprise-madrid-gig-2560574">最后一刻西班牙演出</a>中<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/green-day-tease-playing-dookie-full-upcoming-concert-madrid-2561303">向歌迷透露，他们将完整演绎他们 1994 年的开创性唱片</a>。</p><p>展望未来，绿日乐队上个月在加拿大<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/festival-dete-de-quebec-2023-live-review-the-city-is-the-headliner-3469543">魁北克音乐节上首次</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-green-day-debut-new-song-1981-3471107">推出了一首名为“1981”的新歌</a>。</p><p>这首新歌是在 Green Day 乐队（由主唱兼吉他手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-joe-armstrong">Billie Joe Armstrong</a> 、贝斯手 Mike Durnt 和鼓手 Tré Cool 组成）合同到期后与唱片公司 Reprise Records 分道扬镳之后推出的。</p><p> 2021 年 12 月，他们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/green-day-tease-new-music-recorded-in-london-and-fans-think-it-could-be-next-album-3121786">分享了一段自己在伦敦 RAK 工作室录制音乐的片段</a>，该片段可能是一首新歌。在短视频中，数字“1972”在屏幕上闪现，让粉丝们怀疑这是否是一首新歌或一张全新专辑的名称。</p><p>该乐队发行的最后一张专辑是 2020 年的《Father Of All Motherfuckers》。在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/green-day-father-of-all-review-2605870">一篇四星评论</a>中， <em>《NME》</em>称赞这张唱片是“好老的跪下”。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/green-day-are-teasing-dookie-30th-anniversary-plans-3480467">Green Day 正在调侃“Dookie”30 周年纪念计划的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
